            "heading": "Follow Us on"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_FFnriF": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>We all have that box of gold jewelry sitting in the bank locker, full of pieces collected over the years. You’ve thought about wearing them out for parties or family functions, but they just don’t feel right anymore. The outdated designs have them sitting in that locker for years. </p><p> Life evolves, and so might your taste in jewelry. Whether it’s the <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/wedding-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Wedding Ring\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">wedding</span></a> jewelry passed down through generations, gifts received on special occasions, or ornaments that no longer match your style, many of us have old gold lying unused in our lockers.</p><p>So its time to grab your old gold, and pick out some fresh new designs for yourself, ones that you’ll actually wear. With Lucira Jewelry’s buyback and exchange policy, you can now resell, exchange and get instant buyback value for your old gold and fill your jewelry box with intricate and modern designs from Lucira Jewelry.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_fjmKRF": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Lifetime Exchange: Redesign Your Story, Anytime",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Lifetime Exchange: Redesign Your Story, Anytime</h2><p>Jewelry is meant to evolve with you, not sit forgotten in a locker. With Lucira Jewelry's Lifetime Exchange Policy, you can exchange your jewelry anytime, whether it’s months or years later.</p>",
            "custom_id": "lifetime"
          }
        },
        "image_pjQALn": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Lifetime_Exchange.png"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_m76ykE": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Lifetime Exchange",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Here’s how it works:</h3><ul><li>You get the full 100% of your metal value, be it gold or platinum, at the current market rate.</li><li>You’ll get 100% of your diamond value as well, at the prevailing market rate.</li><li>Based on the evaluation, the exchange credit is deposited into your Lucira Jewelry Wallet.</li><li>Simply use the credit to purchase any new jewelry piece that speaks to you.</li></ul><h3>Key Conditions:</h3><ul><li>The original invoice and certificate are required. If the certificate is missing, a fee of ₹1,500 applies.</li><li>The jewelry must pass Lucira Jewelry’s Quality Inspection.</li><li>Exchange credit cannot be encashed, but it lets you refresh your collection anytime.</li></ul><p>Whether you want to swap a classic <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/solitaire-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Solitaire Rings\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">solitaire ring</span></a> for a contemporary bezel-set ring or upgrade a delicate <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/pendant-necklaces\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Pendant Necklace\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">pendant necklace</span></a> to a bold statement piece, Lucira Jewelry ensures your design always keeps pace with your evolving style.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_WkNqpX": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Buyback: Instant Value, On Your Terms",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Buyback: Instant Value, On Your Terms</h2><p>Sometimes, you just want your investment to work for you in the form of cash. Lucira Jewelry’s fair buyback promise ensures that when you choose to part ways with your jewelry, you do so with confidence.</p>",
            "custom_id": "buyback"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_pUGYXk": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Buyback_50k.png",
            "text": "<h3>Here’s how it works:</h3><ul><li>You get 90% of the metal value, calculated at the current market rate.</li><li>For the sparkle lovers, you get 90% of your diamond’s value, based on market prices.</li><li>The final amount is processed via Razorpay X bank transfer within 15 business days of your final approval.</li></ul><h3>Key Conditions:</h3><ul><li>Your jewelry will need to match its original purchase records and pass our quality check.</li><li>You will also need to provide the certificate. A missing certificate will result in a ₹1,500 deduction.</li><li>Refunds are securely transferred to your registered bank account.</li></ul>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_aGtcb9": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "How to Get Started with Renewing Your Jewelry",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>How to Get Started with Renewing Your Jewelry</h2><h3>Step 1: Contact Us</h3><p>Reach out at support@lucirajewelry.com or chat with us on our website. Share your product details and request a preliminary valuation.</p><h3>Step 2: Receive a Valuation Estimate</h3><p>Our team will assess your jewelry details and provide an approximate valuation based on current gold and diamond prices.</p><h3>Step 3: Secure Pickup from Your Doorstep</h3><p>Once you’re comfortable with the estimate, we’ll arrange a secure pickup from your registered address. Your jewelry is fully insured in transit. A flat shipping fee of ₹750, deducted from your final value, applies.</p><h3>Step 4: Final Valuation & Approval</h3><p>After a complete quality check, we’ll share the final valuation. Approve it within 15 days, and we’ll process your exchange credit or buyback refund. If we don’t hear from you within 15 days, we’ll credit the exchange value to your Lucira Wallet to avoid delays.</p><h3>Step 5: Get Paid or Shop Anew</h3><p>Buyback amount: Bank transfer in 10–15 business days.</p><p>Exchange: Store credits in your Lucira Wallet, valid for 365 days.</p>",
            "custom_id": "how"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qTTh3t": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why Lucira Jewelry’s Exchange & Buyback Policy Stands Out",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Why Lucira Jewelry’s Exchange & Buyback Policy Stands Out</h2><ul><li>100% Value on Exchange: We value your trust as much as your gold and diamonds. No deductions when you exchange for something new.</li><li>90% Fair Buyback: No melting losses, no hidden cuts - just straightforward market value.</li><li>Lifetime Flexibility: No expiry on when you can exchange. Whether it’s a gift from last year or a purchase from five years ago, we’ll honor the market value.</li><li>Secure & Seamless: From insured pickups to safe payouts, we handle everything so you don’t have to worry.</li><li>Sustainably Smart: Repurpose your jewelry, reduce waste, and embrace ethical luxury.</li></ul>",
            "custom_id": "why"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_xDjbx7": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "A Few Important Things to Know",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>A Few Important Things to Know</h2><ul><li>Any discounts or promotional gifts from your original purchase will be adjusted from your final exchange or buyback value.</li><li>If your jewelry has missing certification (e.g., IGI certificate), a ₹1,500 charge applies per missing certificate.</li><li>Our policies apply only to purchases made directly through Lucira Jewelry’s official website or authorized platforms.</li></ul>",
            "custom_id": "important"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_t7fbq7": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Final Word: Your Jewelry, Your Choice, Our Promise",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Final Word: Your Jewelry, Your Choice, Our Promise</h2><p>At <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Lucira Jewelry</span></a>, we believe your jewelry should evolve with you, whether that means redesigning it for your next chapter or redeeming its value when life calls for something else. Our Lifetime Exchange & Buyback Policy is built on transparency, trust, and timeless value.</p><p>So, whether your old gold is waiting to shine again or it’s time to bid it farewell, Lucira Jewelry makes the process seamless, secure, and satisfying.</p>",
            "custom_id": "final"
          }
        }
      },
